
                      ICE Nordic Atari Show intro 

This  little effort came from STe demo masters Inner Circuit  Explorers 
as  one  of the more pleasant surprises from the  Nordic  Atari  Show.. 
Having figured out that ICE were not immediately active on the  Falcon, 
it was nice to see them agin in this nicely done if rather short  debut 
effort here..

ICE starts off with some neato graphics,  a whirlpool picture/logo very 
heavy  on  the  truecolour,  then some new twists on the theme  of  3-D 
donutty objects..

These  ones  are textured,  but with a difference as a  shiny  metallic 
effect is used, and with a bit of lightsourcing thrown in too.. Dare we 
use the new soon to be lazy reviewers buzzword/cliche?? 
