                           **Press Launch!**

11th  September 1996..  Techie-Jargon & Associates are proud to present 
to an eager world,  'ENVIRONMENT MAPPING!'

Ron  Bollocks,  the chief developer of this new word picks up the story 
for Maggie..

"Well, it was touch and go for a time, as early prototypes of this word 
were seen in action at the Hamburg Symposium.. It was the case that Tat 
was  field-testing this word,  and a number of other useful phrases for 
us  at  the  time,  unfortunately most of the other words  and  phrases 
sounded  like Glaswegian drunks after five days with no proper rest  or 
relaxation,  but  'Environment  Mapping' survived the carnage,  and has 
been  refined  by our team into the quality new product  that  you  see 
in front of you today.."

Thank  you  Ron,  and  with that bit of accomplished padding out  of  a 
desperately thin review, we now return you back to the regular text..
